How I style my hair with extensions as a hair stylist! I love the color and blend of these specific extensions, they match my hair color perfectly -  @foxylocks "Mochaccino" 22 inch
STEPS:
1. Brush your hair and extension hair THOROUGHLY
2. Divide hair into sections based on measurement and  number of weft clips on your extension clips (3, 4, 5)
3. Tease the root of your hair before clipping extensions in if your hair is clean. If hair is dirty, skip this step and snap them right in
4. Style in sections and spray with your favorite hairspray 
**PRO TIP: brush hair vertically for a softer wave**
